main_body:
Regulation (EEC) No 1934/93 is hereby amended as follows:
1. in Annex I.C, the information on the provinces of Evias, zone 11, Lakonias, zone 5, Halkidikis, zones 6 and 8 and Kykladon, zone 3, is replaced by the information in the Annex to this Regulation;
2. in Annex II.C:
(a) in Nomos Rethymnou the commune of Platanou is added to zone 12;
(b) in the Nomos Fokidas, the commune of Vinianis is added to zone 6;
3. in Annex II.D:
in the Communidad autĂłnoma de Castilla-La Mancha in the province of Ciudad Real, in zone 4, the commune of Puebla de Don Rodrigo is deleted; it is added to zone 1 of the same province.
